MongoDb is an open source database developed by MongoDb, Inc.
MongoDb stores data in JSON like structure.
It is a NoSql database.
MongoDb used BSON(Binary Javascript Object Notation) to query database.

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

# MysQL #                                            # MongoDb #
=>Table                                            =>Collection
=>Row                                              =>Document
=>Column                                           =>Field

-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Logical Operator
$and-all conditions must be true
condition 1               condition 2               result
T                              T                       T
T                              F                       F
F                              T                       F
F                              F                       F

$or-one conditions must be true
condition 1               condition 2               result
T                              T                       T
T                              F                       T
F                              T                       T
F                              F                       F

$not-all conditions must be true
condition 1                  result
T                              F                      
F                              T                   

